Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Prime corner site on Lytton Road

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are excited to present to market for lease, 1289Lytton Road, Hemmant. A prime corner site situated on main Lytton Road, this site offers two street access and easy access to the Gateway Arterial North and South. This site is also in close proximity to the Port of Brisbane and local amenity.

Some the features of this site include:  

• 400sqm* clearspan warehouse accessed via multiple roller doors 
• Drive through 140sqm* all-weather awning featuring a 1t crane 
• 90sqm* ground floor office with staff amenities + shower (additional mezzanine storage above) 
• Approx. 1,600sm bitumen hardstand fully fenced and secured 
• Dedicated wash bay with oil separator + 3 phase power 
• Excellent signage opportunity fronting Lytton Road 
• Fiber optic installed in the building 
• Property will undergo significant refurbishment 

*Approx.

For further information regarding this opportunity or should you wish to arrange an inspection, please contact Exclusive Agent Ben Lyons of CBRE.

Hemmant is conveniently located approximately 15 kilometres east of Brisbane CBD, midway between the Port of Brisbane and the Gateway Motorway. 14 Luke Street enjoys excellent access to the Brisbane Airport via the Port of Brisbane Motorway and is in walking distance to the Hemmant railway station.  

Unit 1/14 Luke Street is of full concrete tilt panel construction and provides significant internal clearance of between 8 and 10.5 metres.  

Some of the features of this site are:  
•	1,354sqm corporate office accommodation split over two levels
•	2,995sqm high bay warehousing accessed via 4 large (6m) electric roller doors
•	Warehouse is fully sprinkled
•	Huge awning allowing for loading in all-weather conditions
•	Generous hardstand area allowing great truck access and container set down
•	Available immediately
•	Generous exclusive car parks onsite 

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact Exclusive Marketing Agent, Ben Lyons of CBRE.

Located in the highly sought after and easily accessible industrial area of Hemmant, this quality office/warehouse unit is located within minutes drive to the Gateway Motorway connecting to the other major arterials and the greater Brisbane region. Situated approx. 6klms from the Port of Brisbane, approx. 11klms from the Brisbane CBD, this property offers excellent access with ample on-site parking and is ideally suited for a range of businesses looking for a tidy and strategically positioned facility. 

Some of the salient features of this property are: 
•	Modern tilt panel building 
•	550sqm* high bay, clearspan warehouse
•	200sqm* office accommodation offering some open plan and partitioned office space 
•	Showroom style entrance on ground floor 
•	Great natural lighting 
•	Direct exposure to busy Lytton Road 
•	Accessed via three (3) electric container height roller doors 
•	Good access for trucks and container set down 
•	Staff amenities including two toilets 
•	8 exclusive car parks 

For further information regarding this outstanding opportunity or should you wish to arrange an inspection, please contact Agents Ben Lyons or Braiden Farrer of CBRE today.
